# CodeGraph

This repo is indexed with [colbymchenry/codegraph](https://github.com/colbymchenry/codegraph) (local MCP in `.cursor/mcp.json`).

## When to prefer CodeGraph

- Finding where a symbol is defined or used (`scoreThesis`, `useStore`, `buildThesisPortfolio`, etc.)
- Understanding call chains across `src/` and `server/`
- Scoping a change before editing multiple files

Use **CodeGraph MCP tools** first instead of repeated broad `Grep` / `SemanticSearch` when `.codegraph/` exists.

## Maintenance

After large refactors or new modules:

```bash
cd /Users/jaidenrabatin/Projects/thesis && codegraph sync
```

Full rebuild:

```bash
cd /Users/jaidenrabatin/Projects/thesis && codegraph index --force
```

Install / re-index for new machines: `npm run setup:agent-tooling`

Restart Cursor after MCP config changes.
